## URGENT: Missing Return Type Validators - Must Fix First

### Phase 1: Add Missing Return Type Validators (CRITICAL)

**Status: ❌ NOT DONE - This is blocking the build**

All Convex functions are missing required `returns:` validators. This will cause build failures.

